name: 赛德·瓦尔德
introduction: Height	5' 7½" (1.71 m)Mini Bio (1)Syd's talents are multi-dimensional as she is an actress, comedienne, writer and producer. Through her production company that she started in 2014, Beyond My Wildest Dreams Productions, LLC, Syd has written and produced over 30 sketch comedies for her You Tube Channel through the multi-channel network, Maker Studios as a way to showcase her writing and acting style. Syd's sketches have been featured on sites such as: Huffington Post, Cosmopolitan, College Humor and Sports Illustrated, to name a few, and between her original sketches and collaborations with others, she has amassed over 60 million online views. Syd has appeared on network episodic TV shows and been in several films on the SYFY Network, as well as several Feature Films. Syd has also performed stand up comedy at The Comedy Store and The Improv. Syd has studied with many esteemed acting coaches, as well as voice, dialect and voice over coaches. Her hobbies include several forms of dance: salsa, tango and belly dancing.
